        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white mb-4">
          One App. <span class="gradient-text">iPhone, iPad, Mac.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          ThinkBud is a true universal Apple app. iCloud sync via CloudKit keeps every flashcard, mind map, and group chat in lockstep across your devices.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- iPhone -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-8 text-center hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-accent/40 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-2xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 1.5H8.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 3.75v16.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 20.25V3.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H13.5m-3 0V3h3V1.5m-3 0h3m-3 18.75h3" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-2">iPhone</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Optimized for one-handed use, with a Home Screen widget showing your streak and cards due. Snap a photo of a textbook page and have a study kit waiting.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- iPad -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface p-8 text-center hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-accent/40 transition-all duration-300">
