          See <span class="gradient-text">ThinkBud</span> in Action
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted max-w-xl mx-auto">
          A clean, focused interface designed to keep you learning — not fighting the app.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
